Enjoy delicious meals all day long when you dine at one of our on-site restaurants. Offering local and continental dishes, 64/6 is a multi-cuisine buffet restaurant with something for the whole family. You can order delicious vegetarian dishes at Kebab Junction, impress a client at Tatva or dine poolside at 3B’s. Café J is open 24 hours a day, making it the perfect spot for a casual meal, pastries or coffee with colleagues.

Things to Do near Ghaziabad
Our hotel is conveniently located near greater New Delhi attractions, including historic sites like the Red Fort (Lal Quila). Don’t miss these favourites during your stay:

Akshardham - Just 15 minutes away, Akshardham is a large Hindu temple constructed of nearly 6,000 tonnes of pink sandstone. The temple features a 60-acre garden, lifelike dioramas and an evening water show. Please note that phones, cameras and bags are not allowed in the complex.

Connaught Place - Located about 16 kilometres from the hotel, Connaught Place is one of the largest commercial and business centres in New Delhi. While there, you can browse dozens of shops, watch a movie or dine at great restaurants.

Humayun's Tomb - This 16th-century mausoleum is less than 30 minutes from the Country Inn & Suites. Humayun's Tomb boasts impressive marble and red sandstone building materials and is set in a Persian-style garden, making it easy to see why the Taj Mahal was modelled after it.

